An Act relative to the taxation of rolling stock.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 SECTION 1. Section 1 of Chapter 64H of the general laws, as appearing in the 2022
2 Official Edition, is hereby amended by inserting, after the definition of “Retail establishment”,
3 the following new definition:-
4 “Rolling stock”, trucks, tractors, and trailers, used by common carriers to transport goods
5 in interstate commerce.
6 SECTION 2. Section 6 of Chapter 64H of the general laws, as so appearing, is hereby
7 further amended by inserting, after subsection (xx), the following new subsection:
8 “(yy) sales of rolling stock”
